{
  "stem": "15991.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 227.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She taught us, but we did not know of her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, we knew of her private feelings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was not mentioned in school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] It's a difficult question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there was so little from home that made us feel really Jewish, you see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More confusion than definite feelings of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It felt good being in the religious instructions in the temple and going to attending some of the holidays.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was as being in a vacuum because my parents weren't there, my parents never set foot in a, in a synagogue or a temple.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was-- my brother didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was just me being there, somewhere, learning something that the others hadn't learned or didn't know very much about.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why then did your parents send you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their idea was to offer us the possibilities of choosing the religion we wanted to when-- once we were old enough to do so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so they wanted to show me what the Jewish religion was like, and so thereby had me take the religious instruction.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was about the Bible, yes, and about the holy holidays-- some.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think so because we viewed this as being a little bit of a nuisance, also, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, to go there on a Saturday afternoon or Saturday morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, on the other hand, I also felt a little bit of a waste of time, because I think it is very important that it's encouraged at home and talked about, yes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was there from 10 till 13, 12 or 13.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I had one year of private tutoring with some other children whose school had closed, some of my own classmates.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Jewish, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
